      &lt;h2 class=&quot;my-0 mb-[16px] text-ellipsis text-[18px] font-medium text-emphasis&quot;&gt;
        延伸阅读
      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/finance/china/story20250420-6216453&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              英财长：与中国脱钩“非常愚蠢”  支持希音赴英上市
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;英财长：与中国脱钩“非常愚蠢”  支持希音赴英上市&quot; title=&quot;英财长：与中国脱钩“非常愚蠢”  支持希音赴英上市&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/397d4144fc9a89db6bf5cda97871ba35b52ef4bba0c214d2110d8e6705fe8bd6&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
